{"title":"如何用笔记本电脑做服务器","uid":"cc4fef36b4bac0f396377160cbe0e0d0","slug":"内网服务器","date":"2021-10-06T04:27:41.000Z","updated":"2021-10-06T14:05:05.283Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/内网服务器.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://bu.dusays.com/2021/10/06/b3627457a02aa.jpg","content":"<p>首先，我的笔记本是14年以4200的价格买的，大概到20年初还可以打使命召唤OL（现已停运），然后放家里不用了，就开始不行了，老觉得卡。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">配置：\n品牌：神舟精盾K480D-i7 1T\nCPU：酷睿i7-4710mq\n内存：6+6G\n显卡：GeForce 840M\n硬盘：1T<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>再长达6年的使用时间里，除了键盘换过一次外（都磨秃噜皮了），没什么大毛病，我觉得神舟质量还行，当然过保修就坏的人可以使劲黑。。。。<br>上老伙计图片：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2021/10/06/56387e5110c2e.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0345.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2021/10/06/1c14e9ec43eb5.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0346.jpg\"></p>\n<p>那么，今天就再让他发光发热</p>\n<p>之前用的服务器系统是windows server 2016，安好了以后有点卡，<br>昨天折腾了一下，换到centos7.9系统了</p>\n<p>网上如果搜如何安装<code>centos7</code>，那么十有八九出来得是用一个叫<code>VMware</code>虚拟机软件安装的。<br>但是直接在一台笔记本上如何安装centos7呢？<br>下面记录一下过程。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>准备工具<br>1.一个U盘<br>2.一个centos7.x镜像文件<br>3.一个叫<code>UltraISO</code>的软件，可以把镜像文件制作成u盘启动。</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>下面是详细步骤：</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>到centos官网<a href=\"https://www.centos.org下载镜像,选择国内镜像站下载/\">https://www.centos.org下载镜像，选择国内镜像站下载</a><br>  或者如果你的电脑是x86—64位的<br>centos7.9 迅雷种子：<a href=\"https://mirrors.bfsu.edu.cn/centos/7.9.2009/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-2009.torrent\">https://mirrors.bfsu.edu.cn/centos/7.9.2009/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-2009.torrent</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>centos8.4 迅雷种子：<a href=\"http://mirrors.163.com/centos/8.4.2105/isos/x86_64/CentOS-8.4.2105-x86_64-boot.iso.manifest\">http://mirrors.163.com/centos/8.4.2105/isos/x86_64/CentOS-8.4.2105-x86_64-boot.iso.manifest</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>下载UltraISO,地址：<a href=\"https://cn.ultraiso.net/xiazai.html\">https://cn.ultraiso.net/xiazai.html</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>用管理员身份打开，再软件本地目录找到下载的iso，在右边窗口双击加载，然后点击软件菜单上的启动-写入硬盘映像，等待制作好U盘启动。</p>\n<p>或者看这个教程 <a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/larry-luo/p/11102321.html\">https://www.cnblogs.com/larry-luo/p/11102321.html</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>下一步，就是从u盘加载系统，关机后，进入bios选择U 盘为第一启动项，保存退出，如果你能成功的从U盘加载，那么你会看到下面这个界面</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2021/10/06/30b6d64b75392.png\" alt=\"1.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>根据提示按<code>tab</code>键（第一次，我是根据某教程安装了没有图形界面的centos，完全不会用啊）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>然后你就会进入centos引导安装界面，没有什么上面教程中的按e编辑什么的</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2021/10/06/5fb9c8478e8a7.png\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n<p>点击软件选择，选择Gnome 桌面，然后在右边选择几个重要的功能</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>可以先不设置网络和主机名</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>完善全部信息后，点击开始安装</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装过程中设置<code>root用户名</code>和<code>密码</code>，创建用户不需要设置</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>等待好一会，安装好了，点击重启，重启前要拔下u盘，不然又进安装界面了</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>我重启后一直闪光标，强制关机，再开机顺利进入centos图形操作界面</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/10/06/neiwangfuwuqi/IMG_0343.jpg\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>在右上角设置无线网连接，</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在左上角应用程序里找到浏览器看能否上网，再找到终端，进入终端命令，安装宝塔面板</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Centos安装命令如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -y <span class=\"token function\">wget</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">wget</span> -O install.sh http://download.bt.cn/install/install_6.0.sh <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">sh</span> install.sh<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>安装好面板后，终端会给出面板用户名和密码，如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/10/06/neiwangfuwuqi/IMG_0344-2.jpg\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>然后在家里另外一台电脑上打开内网地址就进入宝塔登录界面了，设置一下进入控制面板</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/10/06/neiwangfuwuqi/2.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>根据提示一键安装推荐的软件</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>点击网站，选择添加站点，域名写你的笔记本的内网ip地址，这里提醒一下，为了避免笔记本电脑每次获取不同的IP，到路由器里面把<code>IP地址和笔记本mac地址</code>绑定，这样电脑每次都会获取<code>192.168.0.104</code>这个地址，而不是路由器随机分配的地址</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><p>建好站点后，到浏览器中输入192.168.0.104看能否访问</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>能正确访问的话，到宝塔面板选择-文件-www-wwwroot-192.168.0.104这个文件夹下，把所有文件都删了，点击上传，把hexo博客的public文件夹下的所有文件上传，要点进public文件夹，也就是192.168.0.104文件夹下有index.html和404.html等文件，而不是public文件夹</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>然后就在内网得到了一个静态博客</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/10/06/neiwangfuwuqi/1%E3%80%82png\"></p>\n<p>如果不想要纯静态博客，那么可以用宝塔面板的一键安装Wordpress，安好后，根据wordpress提示操作。</p>\n<p>试一下ftp和其他功能。</p>\n<p>总结：遇到问题多上网搜索一下，遥想当年花钱请人装系统到现在<code>徒手</code>建一个服务器，时光不待人,岁月催人老啊</p>\n","text":"首先，我的笔记本是14年以4200的价格买的，大概到20年初还可以打使命召唤OL（现已停运），然后放家里不用了，就开始不行了，老觉得卡。 配置： 品牌：神舟精盾K480D-i7 1T CPU：酷睿i7-4710mq 内存：6+6G 显卡：GeForce 840M 硬盘：1T 再长...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"其他","slug":"其他","count":39,"path":"api/categories/其他.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"服务器","slug":"服务器","count":1,"path":"api/tags/服务器.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"花开","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/medias/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"我不会向暴力犯罪屈服。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/","stackoverflow":"https://stackoverflow.com","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"如何搭建图床","uid":"bcc8228c5c353864d4a9be945873d7ba","slug":"搭建图床","date":"2021-10-08T11:24:20.000Z","updated":"2021-10-19T16:42:12.445Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/搭建图床.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/10/08/dajiantuchuang/server-2160321.jpg","text":"本篇博客记录我在笔记本上搭建图床服务器的过程先上GitHub上找找吧开源的项目吧 发现两个项目仓库的Star星星数量挺多的，就 直接拿走走吧。 ImgURL地址：https://github.com/helloxz/imgurl 兰空图床(Lsky Pro) :地址：https:...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":363,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"其他","slug":"其他","count":39,"path":"api/categories/其他.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"搭建图床","slug":"搭建图床","count":1,"path":"api/tags/搭建图床.json"}],"author":{"name":"花开","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/medias/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"我不会向暴力犯罪屈服。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/","stackoverflow":"https://s